This template is used to produce a phonemic representation (using the [[IPA]] system) of Arabic words or sounds, using natural spelling to avoid the need to search for the correct phonetic symbols. The result is wikilinked to [[Help:IPA for Arabic]]. Optionally, an audio file can also be specified.

===用法===
參數最多不能超過50個。

正常用法：
*<tt><nowiki>{{IPAc-ar|sh|u|k|r|a|n}}</nowiki></tt> produces {{IPAc-ar|sh|u|k|r|a|n}}
*<tt><nowiki>{{IPAc-ar|S|a|d|ii|q|ii}}</nowiki></tt> produces {{IPAc-ar|S|a|d|ii|q|ii}}

